    "text": "Usage of this is just:\n```\t&lt;style&gt;\n\t\t.test {\n\t\t\twidth: 100%;\n\t\t\tbackground: var(--dial-bg, pink);\n\t\t\tborder: 2px var(--dial-border, solid);\n\t\t\tbox-sizing: border-box;\n\t\t\tpadding: var(--dial-padding, 16px);\n\t\t}\n\t&lt;/style&gt;\n\t&lt;css-lab dials=\"\n\t\tbg: pink|hotpink|yellow;\n\t\tpadding: initial | 8px | 16px;\n\t\tborder: solid | dashed;\n\t\"&gt;\n\t  &lt;div class=\"test\"&gt;Hello world!&lt;/div&gt;\n\t&lt;/css-lab&gt;```\nAlthough, it will likely change a lot over time, but I am trying to make it as simple as possible to use for myself.",
    "team": "T5TCAFTA9",
    "thread_ts": "1740825868.873509",
    "parent_user_id": "U087592N6HE",
    "blocks": [
      {
        "type": "rich_text",
        "block_id": "MInlc",
        "elements": [
          {
            "type": "rich_text_section",
            "elements": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Usage of this is just:\n"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "rich_text_preformatted",
            "elements": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "\t<style>\n\t\t.test {\n\t\t\twidth: 100%;\n\t\t\tbackground: var(--dial-bg, pink);\n\t\t\tborder: 2px var(--dial-border, solid);\n\t\t\tbox-sizing: border-box;\n\t\t\tpadding: var(--dial-padding, 16px);\n\t\t}\n\t</style>\n\t<css-lab dials=\"\n\t\tbg: pink|hotpink|yellow;\n\t\tpadding: initial | 8px | 16px;\n\t\tborder: solid | dashed;\n\t\">\n\t  <div class=\"test\">Hello world!</div>\n\t</css-lab>"
              }
            ],
            "border": 0
          },
          {
            "type": "rich_text_section",
            "elements": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Although, it will likely change a lot over time, but I am trying to make it as simple as possible to use for myself."
