  {
    "text": "And the way it works in our design system. The context is rather different, where we want to show the generated code to use for every permutation, but also not complete in some ways, and is less about exploration (no two-way feedback from the controls). But we're pretty happy with how it works, and even saw other design systems adopt a few things from our design &amp; implementation (with explicit mentions).",
